## Known Issues/Limitations
- SQL injection risk (use PreparedStatements for production).
- No user authentication (add login system next?).

## Future Enhancements
- Email boarding passes (JavaMail API).
- Admin reports (JasperReports).
- Mobile app version (Android/JavaFX).

